## F10 — Variants: complete, none invented

```
Figma: default | hover | active | disabled | loading
Code:  default | hover | active | disabled | loading

Missing = VIOLATION. Extra invented = VIOLATION.
```

---

## Exception Protocol

| Situation | Action |
|---|---|
| Figma frame incomplete / placeholder | STOP → ask designer to complete |
| Two identical components differ by 1px | STOP → report to designer → await decision |
| Font license unavailable | STOP → ask client to provide or purchase |
| Figma and brief contradict | STOP → ask which is source of truth |
